    <div begin="00:27.430" end="04:01.600">
      <p begin="00:27.430" end="00:29.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:27.430" end="00:27.570">In</span><span begin="00:27.610" end="00:27.820">to</span> <span begin="00:27.820" end="00:27.930">the</span> <span begin="00:28.000" end="00:28.290">bro</span><span begin="00:28.360" end="00:28.800">ken</span> <span begin="00:28.800" end="00:29.020">mir</span><span begin="00:29.020" end="00:29.570">ror</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">踏入那破碎的残镜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">踏入那破碎的殘鏡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">砕け散った鏡の中へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">산산조각 난 거울 속으로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans le miroir brisé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hacia el espejo roto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hinein in den zerbrochenen Spiegel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para dentro do espelho quebrado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Шагая в разбитое зеркало</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nello specchio infranto</span></p>
      <p begin="00:30.370" end="00:34.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:30.370" end="00:30.800">All</span> <span begin="00:30.800" end="00:31.030">light</span> <span begin="00:31.030" end="00:31.110">i</span><span begin="00:31.110" end="00:31.220">s</span> <span begin="00:31.220" end="00:31.450">lo</span><span begin="00:31.450" end="00:31.570">st</span> <span begin="00:31.570" end="00:31.790">wi</span><span begin="00:31.790" end="00:32.210">thin</span> <span begin="00:32.210" end="00:32.820">the</span> <span begin="00:33.170" end="00:34.210">ma</span><span begin="00:34.210" end="00:34.330">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所有的光芒迷失于迷局之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所有的光芒迷失於迷局之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">迷宮にて全ての光は失われる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미궁 속에서 모든 빛을 잃었네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toute lumière se perd dans le labyrinthe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Toda la luz se pierde en el laberinto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles Licht geht im Labyrinth verloren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda a luz está perdida dentro do labirinto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Весь свет меркнет в этом лабиринте</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutta la luce è perduta nel labirinto</span></p>
      <p begin="00:35.630" end="00:40.270" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:35.630" end="00:35.930">Like</span> <span begin="00:35.990" end="00:36.320">e</span><span begin="00:36.400" end="00:36.680">cho</span><span begin="00:36.680" end="00:36.740">es</span> <span begin="00:36.790" end="00:37.080">di</span><span begin="00:37.080" end="00:37.180">s</span><span begin="00:37.180" end="00:37.910">sol</span><span begin="00:37.970" end="00:38.420">ving</span> <span begin="00:38.420" end="00:38.570">in</span> <span begin="00:38.770" end="00:39.640">si</span><span begin="00:39.640" end="00:40.140">len</span><span begin="00:40.140" end="00:40.270">ce</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宛如回音在死寂中消融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">宛如迴音在死寂中消融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">静寂に溶けゆく木霊のように</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">침묵 속에 녹아드는 메아리처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme des échos se dissolvant dans le silence</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como ecos disolviéndose en el silencio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie Echos die sich in der Stille auflösen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como ecos se dissolvendo no silêncio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно эхо растворяющееся в безмолвии</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come echi che si dissolvono nel silenzio</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.380" end="00:42.890" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:40.380" end="00:40.620">Fal</span><span begin="00:40.620" end="00:40.720">len</span> <span begin="00:40.720" end="00:41.350">scroll</span><span begin="00:41.350" end="00:41.440">s</span> <span begin="00:41.440" end="00:41.560">are</span> <span begin="00:41.560" end="00:41.800">cal</span><span begin="00:41.800" end="00:41.900">ling</span> <span begin="00:41.980" end="00:42.890">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">散落的古卷正呼唤着我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">散落的古卷正呼喚著我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">堕ちた巻物が私を呼んでいる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바닥에 떨어진 고서들이 나를 부르고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les parchemins déchus m'appellent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los pergaminos caídos me llaman</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gefallene Schriftrollen rufen nach mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pergaminhos caídos estão me chamando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Павшие древние свитки взывают ко мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le pergamene cadute mi chiamano</span></p>
      <p begin="00:43.580" end="00:48.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:43.580" end="00:43.890">Grant</span> <span begin="00:44.000" end="00:44.320">me</span> <span begin="00:44.410" end="00:44.700">more</span> <span begin="00:44.780" end="00:45.110">than</span> <span begin="00:45.180" end="00:45.380">e</span><span begin="00:45.530" end="00:46.170">ter</span><span begin="00:46.170" end="00:46.490">ni</span><span begin="00:46.690" end="00:48.420">ty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">赐予我超越永恒的真谛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">賜予我超越永恆的真諦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">永遠以上のものを私に与えよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">영원 그 이상의 것을 내게 내려주소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Accorde-moi plus que l'éternité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Concédeme más que la eternidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gewähre mir mehr als nur die Ewigkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Conceda-me mais do que a eternidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даруй мне нечто большее чем вечность</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Concedimi più dell'eternità</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.920" end="00:52.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:49.920" end="00:50.130">E</span><span begin="00:50.360" end="00:51.200">ter</span><span begin="00:51.200" end="00:51.400">ni</span><span begin="00:51.580" end="00:52.710">ty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">永恒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">永恆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">永遠を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">영원을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'éternité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La eternidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Ewigkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eternidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чем вечность</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eternità</span></p>
      <p begin="00:55.960" end="00:59.600" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:55.960" end="00:56.360">Take</span> <span begin="00:56.410" end="00:57.510">me</span> <span begin="00:57.570" end="00:57.800">to</span> <span begin="00:57.970" end="00:59.600">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">带我去见证</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">帶我去見證</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を導いて見せてくれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 이끌어 보여주소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Emmène-moi voir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Llévame a ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nimm mich mit um zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Leve-me para ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволь мне узреть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Portami a vedere</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00.800" end="01:05.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:00.800" end="01:01.210">Blin</span><span begin="01:01.260" end="01:01.480">ding</span> <span begin="01:01.590" end="01:02.630">tru</span><span begin="01:02.630" end="01:02.800">th</span> <span begin="01:02.800" end="01:03.530">yet</span> <span begin="01:03.580" end="01:03.890">to</span> <span begin="01:04.020" end="01:04.390">be</span><span begin="01:04.390" end="01:05.760">lieve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">令人目眩却难以置信的真相</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">令人目眩卻難以置信的真相</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">未だ信じ難き目も眩むほどの真実を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아직 믿기 힘든 눈부신 진실을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vérité aveuglante à laquelle il faut encore croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La verdad cegadora aún por creer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Blendende Wahrheit an die es noch zu glauben gilt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A verdade cegante em que ainda hei de crer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ослепительную истину в которую еще предстоит поверить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una verità accecante ancora da credere</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.920" end="01:12.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:05.920" end="01:06.290">Drown</span> <span begin="01:06.380" end="01:06.770">me</span> <span begin="01:06.770" end="01:07.140">in</span> <span begin="01:07.140" end="01:07.490">the</span> <span begin="01:07.560" end="01:12.000">deep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将我沉溺于深渊之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將我沉溺於深淵之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を深淵に溺れさせてくれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 저 깊은 심연에 가라앉히소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Noie-moi dans les profondeurs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahógame en las profundidades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ertränke mich in der Tiefe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Afogue-me nas profundezas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Утопи меня в пучине</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Annegami nel profondo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:12.390" end="01:16.700" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:12.390" end="01:12.630">Lo</span><span begin="01:12.630" end="01:12.780">st</span> <span begin="01:12.780" end="01:13.170">wi</span><span begin="01:13.200" end="01:13.550">thin</span> <span begin="01:13.630" end="01:13.910">my</span> <span begin="01:14.040" end="01:14.680">me</span><span begin="01:14.680" end="01:14.780">m</span><span begin="01:14.780" end="01:14.970">o</span><span begin="01:14.970" end="01:16.560">rie</span><span begin="01:16.560" end="01:16.700">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迷失在我的记忆深处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迷失在我的記憶深處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">記憶の中に迷い込み</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기억 속에서 길을 잃은 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Perdu dans mes souvenirs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Perdido en mis recuerdos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verloren in meinen Erinnerungen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perdido dentro de minhas memórias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заблудившегося в собственных воспоминаниях</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perso nei miei ricordi</span></p>
      <p begin="01:17.140" end="01:20.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:17.140" end="01:17.360">The</span> <span begin="01:17.360" end="01:17.560">S</span><span begin="01:17.560" end="01:18.390">tar</span> <span begin="01:18.390" end="01:18.590">will</span> <span begin="01:18.790" end="01:19.910">set</span> <span begin="01:20.010" end="01:20.290">me</span> <span begin="01:20.400" end="01:20.760">free</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">星辰终将赐我解脱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星辰終將賜我解脫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あの星が私を解き放つだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저 별이 나를 해방하리라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'Étoile me libérera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La Estrella me liberará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Stern wird mich befreien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A Estrela me libertará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Звезда дарует мне свободу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La Stella mi libererà</span></p>
      <p begin="01:32.740" end="01:36.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:32.740" end="01:33.110">Set</span> <span begin="01:33.170" end="01:33.480">me</span> <span begin="01:33.570" end="01:36.790">free!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">赐我解脱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">賜我解脫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を解き放て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 해방하리라!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Libère-moi !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Libérame!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mich befreien!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me libertará!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дарует мне свободу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Liberami</span></p>
      <p begin="01:47.120" end="01:50.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:47.120" end="01:47.360">异</span><span begin="01:47.360" end="01:47.560">日</span><span begin="01:47.560" end="01:47.760">的</span><span begin="01:47.760" end="01:47.990">倒</span><span begin="01:47.990" end="01:48.390">影</span> <span begin="01:48.390" end="01:48.570">不</span><span begin="01:48.570" end="01:48.720">断</span><span begin="01:48.790" end="01:49.180">在</span><span begin="01:49.180" end="01:49.510">溶</span><span begin="01:49.580" end="01:50.020">解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Reflections of another day constantly dissolve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">異日の幻影 絶えず溶けゆく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다른 날의 환영은 끊임없이 녹아내리고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les reflets des jours anciens ne cessent de se dissoudre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los reflejos de días ajenos se disuelven sin cesar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Spiegelungen vergangener Tage lösen sich unaufhörlich auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Os reflexos de dias passados dissolvem-se incessantemente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отражения минувших дней непрестанно тают</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I riflessi di giorni lontani si dissolvono senza sosta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yi ri de dao ying bu duan zai rong jie</span></p>
      <p begin="01:50.430" end="01:53.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:50.430" end="01:50.600">模</span><span begin="01:50.600" end="01:50.800">糊</span><span begin="01:50.800" end="01:50.950">的</span><span begin="01:50.990" end="01:51.220">执</span><span begin="01:51.220" end="01:51.580">念</span> <span begin="01:51.580" end="01:51.790">回</span><span begin="01:51.790" end="01:51.940">荡</span><span begin="01:51.980" end="01:52.360">在</span><span begin="01:52.360" end="01:52.740">耳</span><span begin="01:52.810" end="01:53.160">边</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Blurred obsessions echo by the ear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">曖昧なる執念 耳の畔に木霊す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흐릿한 집념만이 귓가에 맴도네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une obsession floue résonne à mes oreilles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las vagas obsesiones resuenan en mis oídos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verschwommene Obsessionen hallen in meinen Ohren wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Uma obsessão turva ecoa nos meus ouvidos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смутная одержимость эхом отдается в ушах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vaghe ossessioni riecheggiano all'orecchio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mo hu de zhi nian hui dang zai er bian</span></p>
      <p begin="01:53.600" end="01:56.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:53.600" end="01:53.760">割</span><span begin="01:53.790" end="01:53.950">碎</span><span begin="01:54.010" end="01:54.150">命</span><span begin="01:54.200" end="01:54.400">的</span><span begin="01:54.420" end="01:54.810">鳞</span><span begin="01:54.810" end="01:55.140">片</span> <span begin="01:55.230" end="01:55.400">模</span><span begin="01:55.400" end="01:55.570">糊</span><span begin="01:55.570" end="01:55.690">了</span><span begin="01:55.730" end="01:55.980">谁</span><span begin="01:55.980" end="01:56.400">的</span><span begin="01:56.400" end="01:56.690">眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Slicing the scales of fate blurring whose eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">命の鱗を切り刻み 誰が眼を霞ませたか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">운명의 비늘을 베어내어, 그 누구의 눈을 흐리게 하는가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tranchant les écailles du destin brouillant le regard de qui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cortando las escamas del destino nublando los ojos de quién</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerschlitzte Schuppen des Schicksals wessen Augen haben sie verschleiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cortando em pedaços as escamas da vida borrando os olhos de quem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рассекая чешую судьбы чьи взоры она затмевает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Frantumando le scaglie della vita la vista di chi si è offuscata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ge sui ming de lin pian mo hu le shui de yan</span></p>
      <p begin="01:56.790" end="01:59.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:56.790" end="01:56.960">饮</span><span begin="01:56.960" end="01:57.160">下</span><span begin="01:57.160" end="01:57.340">这</span><span begin="01:57.400" end="01:57.600">孤</span><span begin="01:57.600" end="01:57.930">绝</span> <span begin="01:57.970" end="01:58.220">叩</span><span begin="01:58.220" end="01:58.330">问</span><span begin="01:58.370" end="01:58.590">苍</span><span begin="01:58.590" end="01:58.800">穹</span><span begin="01:58.800" end="01:59.180">凛</span><span begin="01:59.180" end="01:59.660">冽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drinking down this utter isolation questioning the freezing firmament</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この孤絶を飲み干し 凛烈たる蒼穹に問う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 지독한 고독을 들이마시고, 매서운 창공에 묻노라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Buvant cet isolement absolu j'interroge le firmament glacial</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Bebiendo esta desolación absoluta interrogando al firmamento helado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich trinke diese absolute Einsamkeit und befrage das eisige Himmelsgewölbe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Bebendo este isolamento absoluto questionando o gélido firmamento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Испив чашу абсолютного одиночества я вопрошаю ледяные небеса</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Bevendo questa solitudine assoluta interrogando la gelida volta celeste</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yin xia zhe gu jue kou wen cang qiong lin lie</span></p>
      <p begin="02:00.000" end="02:02.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:00.000" end="02:00.180">漫</span><span begin="02:00.220" end="02:00.370">漫</span><span begin="02:00.390" end="02:00.530">的</span><span begin="02:00.570" end="02:00.820">长</span><span begin="02:00.820" end="02:01.140">路</span> <span begin="02:01.170" end="02:01.350">求</span><span begin="02:01.380" end="02:01.530">索</span><span begin="02:01.580" end="02:01.770">道</span><span begin="02:01.800" end="02:01.930">阻</span><span begin="02:01.960" end="02:02.350">且</span><span begin="02:02.380" end="02:02.790">艰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The boundless long road the path of seeking blocked and arduous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">漫々たる長路 求索の道は阻まれ険し</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아득히 머나먼 길, 진리를 구하는 길은 험난하기만 한데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur cette route interminable la quête est semée d'embûches</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El largo e interminable camino la búsqueda es ardua y llena de obstáculos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein endlos langer Weg meine Suche ist versperrt und beschwerlich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No longo caminho sem fim a busca é árdua e bloqueada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Долог мой путь и терниста дорога исканий</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lungo la strada infinita la via della ricerca è ardua e ostacolata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">man man de chang lu qiu suo dao zu qie jian</span></p>
      <p begin="02:03.160" end="02:05.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:03.160" end="02:03.340">踏</span><span begin="02:03.380" end="02:03.610">碎</span><span begin="02:03.610" end="02:03.760">了</span><span begin="02:03.810" end="02:04.010">光</span><span begin="02:04.010" end="02:04.390">阴</span> <span begin="02:04.390" end="02:04.590">无</span><span begin="02:04.590" end="02:04.790">法</span><span begin="02:04.830" end="02:04.970">回</span><span begin="02:05.000" end="02:05.150">到</span><span begin="02:05.200" end="02:05.580">从</span><span begin="02:05.580" end="02:05.930">前</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trampling time to pieces unable to return to the past</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">光陰を踏み砕き 往時へは戻れず</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">세월을 짓밟고 부수어도 예전으로 돌아갈 순 없구나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Brisant le temps sous mes pas impossible de retourner au passé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pisoteando el tiempo es imposible volver al pasado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Zeit zerschmetternd kann ich nicht in die Vergangenheit zurückkehren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esmagando o tempo sob os pés incapaz de voltar ao passado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Растоптав само время я не в силах вернуться в прошлое</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Calpestando il tempo impossibile fare ritorno al passato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ta sui le guang yin wu fa hui dao cong qian</span></p>
      <p begin="02:06.400" end="02:11.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:06.400" end="02:06.820">坠</span><span begin="02:06.820" end="02:07.180">入</span><span begin="02:07.180" end="02:07.370">这</span><span begin="02:07.570" end="02:08.000">星</span><span begin="02:08.000" end="02:08.310">河</span> <span begin="02:08.390" end="02:08.620">只</span><span begin="02:08.620" end="02:08.760">为</span><span begin="02:08.790" end="02:09.150">揭</span><span begin="02:09.190" end="02:09.560">开</span><span begin="02:09.600" end="02:09.880">这</span><span begin="02:09.970" end="02:10.390">天</span><span begin="02:10.810" end="02:11.600">地</span><span begin="02:11.600" end="02:11.990">间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Falling into this river of stars only to unveil this space between heaven and earth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この星河に墜ちるは 唯この天地を解き明かす為</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 은하수에 몸을 던지는 건, 오직 이 천지간의 이치를 밝히기 위함이니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Plongeant dans ce fleuve d'étoiles juste pour dévoiler les secrets entre Ciel et Terre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cayendo en esta galaxia solo para desvelar el secreto entre el cielo y la tierra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich stürze in diesen Sternenfluss nur um diese Welt zwischen Himmel und Erde zu enthüllen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Caindo neste rio de estrelas apenas para desvendar este espaço entre o céu e a terra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Падая в эту звездную реку лишь ради того чтобы приоткрыть тайну мироздания</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Precipitando in questo fiume di stelle solo per svelare i segreti tra cielo e terra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zhui ru zhe xing he zhi wei jie kai zhe tian di jian</span></p>
      <p begin="02:17.920" end="02:20.550" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:17.920" end="02:18.320">A</span><span begin="02:18.410" end="02:19.010">ban</span><span begin="02:19.010" end="02:19.490">do</span><span begin="02:19.490" end="02:19.600">n</span> <span begin="02:19.600" end="02:20.020">my</span><span begin="02:20.190" end="02:20.550">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">摒弃自我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">摒棄自我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">己を捨て去り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 자신을 저버리고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">M'abandonner moi-même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me abandono a mí mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gebe mich selbst auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Abandono a mim mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отвергая самого себя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Abbandono me stesso</span></p>
      <p begin="02:20.830" end="02:24.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:20.830" end="02:21.130">Let</span> <span begin="02:21.180" end="02:21.500">the</span> <span begin="02:21.550" end="02:22.040">fai</span><span begin="02:22.040" end="02:22.150">th</span> <span begin="02:22.160" end="02:22.650">go</span> <span begin="02:22.740" end="02:24.430">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">任凭信仰坍塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">任憑信仰坍塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">信仰を沈めよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">신념이 무너지게 두어라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisser la foi sombrer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dejo que la fe caiga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lasse den Glauben untergehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixo a fé afundar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволяя вере угаснуть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lascio cadere la fede</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.720" end="02:26.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:24.720" end="02:25.280">See</span><span begin="02:25.350" end="02:25.920">king</span> <span begin="02:25.970" end="02:26.530">ho</span><span begin="02:26.570" end="02:26.640">pe</span><span begin="02:26.640" end="02:26.930">le</span><span begin="02:26.930" end="02:26.990">ss</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在绝望之中寻觅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在絕望之中尋覓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">希望なきを求めて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">절망 속을 헤매며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cherchant le désespoir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Buscando sin esperanza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Suche hoffnungslos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Buscando sem esperanças</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ища в безнадежности</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cercando senza speranza</span></p>
      <p begin="02:27.210" end="02:31.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:27.210" end="02:27.500">How</span> <span begin="02:27.570" end="02:27.890">the</span> <span begin="02:27.950" end="02:28.450">fa</span><span begin="02:28.450" end="02:28.520">te</span> <span begin="02:28.560" end="02:29.220">go</span> <span begin="02:29.220" end="02:31.050">on</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">命运将如何延续</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">命運將如何延續</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">運命は如何にして進むのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">운명은 어떻게 이어지는가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comment le destin continue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cómo el destino sigue adelante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie das Schicksal weitergeht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como o destino prossegue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То как продолжится судьба</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come va avanti il destino</span></p>
      <p begin="02:31.950" end="02:35.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:31.950" end="02:32.370">Take</span> <span begin="02:32.430" end="02:33.520">me</span> <span begin="02:33.600" end="02:33.810">to</span> <span begin="02:33.990" end="02:35.680">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">带我去见证</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">帶我去見證</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を導いて見せてくれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 이끌어 보여주소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Emmène-moi voir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Llévame a ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nimm mich mit um zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Leve-me para ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволь мне узреть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Portami a vedere</span></p>
      <p begin="02:36.790" end="02:41.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:36.790" end="02:37.200">Blin</span><span begin="02:37.250" end="02:37.490">ding</span> <span begin="02:37.580" end="02:38.620">tru</span><span begin="02:38.620" end="02:38.810">th</span> <span begin="02:38.810" end="02:39.540">yet</span> <span begin="02:39.570" end="02:39.890">to</span> <span begin="02:40.000" end="02:40.390">be</span><span begin="02:40.390" end="02:41.760">lieve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">令人目眩却难以置信的真相</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">令人目眩卻難以置信的真相</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">未だ信じ難き目も眩むほどの真実を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아직 믿기 힘든 눈부신 진실을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vérité aveuglante à laquelle il faut encore croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La verdad cegadora aún por creer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Blendende Wahrheit an die es noch zu glauben gilt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A verdade cegante em que ainda hei de crer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ослепительную истину в которую еще предстоит поверить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una verità accecante ancora da credere</span></p>
      <p begin="02:41.930" end="02:47.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:41.930" end="02:42.280">Drown</span> <span begin="02:42.370" end="02:42.760">me</span> <span begin="02:42.760" end="02:43.130">in</span> <span begin="02:43.150" end="02:43.450">the</span> <span begin="02:43.560" end="02:47.990">deep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将我沉溺于深渊之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將我沉溺於深淵之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を深淵に溺れさせてくれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 저 깊은 심연에 가라앉히소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Noie-moi dans les profondeurs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahógame en las profundidades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ertränke mich in der Tiefe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Afogue-me nas profundezas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Утопи меня в пучине</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Annegami nel profondo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.400" end="02:52.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:48.400" end="02:48.620">Lo</span><span begin="02:48.620" end="02:48.780">st</span> <span begin="02:48.780" end="02:49.160">wi</span><span begin="02:49.200" end="02:49.570">thin</span> <span begin="02:49.630" end="02:49.920">my</span> <span begin="02:50.040" end="02:50.690">me</span><span begin="02:50.690" end="02:50.810">m</span><span begin="02:50.810" end="02:50.960">o</span><span begin="02:50.960" end="02:52.540">rie</span><span begin="02:52.540" end="02:52.690">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迷失在我的记忆深处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迷失在我的記憶深處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">記憶の中に迷い込み</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기억 속에서 길을 잃은 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Perdu dans mes souvenirs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Perdido en mis recuerdos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verloren in meinen Erinnerungen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perdido dentro de minhas memórias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заблудившегося в собственных воспоминаниях</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perso nei miei ricordi</span></p>
