      <p begin="03:12.300" end="03:18.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="03:12.300" end="03:12.550">The</span> <span begin="03:12.550" end="03:12.720">S</span><span begin="03:12.720" end="03:13.500">tar</span> <span begin="03:13.500" end="03:13.740">will</span> <span begin="03:13.930" end="03:14.660">set</span> <span begin="03:14.760" end="03:15.310">me</span> <span begin="03:15.540" end="03:18.760">free</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">星辰终将赐我解脱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星辰終將賜我解脫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あの星が私を解き放つだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저 별이 나를 해방하리라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'Étoile me libérera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La Estrella me liberará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Stern wird mich befreien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A Estrela me libertará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Звезда дарует мне свободу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La Stella mi libererà</span></p>
      <p begin="03:20.380" end="03:22.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="03:20.380" end="03:20.680">My</span> <span begin="03:20.760" end="03:21.260">de</span><span begin="03:21.260" end="03:21.370">s</span><span begin="03:21.370" end="03:21.850">ti</span><span begin="03:21.930" end="03:22.450">ny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的宿命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的宿命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我が宿命よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나의 운명이여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon destin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Schicksal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Meu destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Моя судьба</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mio destino</span></p>
      <p begin="03:29.510" end="03:36.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="03:29.510" end="03:29.870">天</span><span begin="03:29.940" end="03:30.280">地</span><span begin="03:30.350" end="03:30.650">间</span> <span begin="03:30.750" end="03:31.100">生</span><span begin="03:31.140" end="03:31.490">与</span><span begin="03:31.560" end="03:36.080">灭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Between heaven and earth life and extinction</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">天地の間 生と滅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">천지간 생(生)과 멸(滅)이여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Entre Ciel et Terre naissance et extinction</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Entre el cielo y la tierra la vida y la extinción</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zwischen Himmel und Erde Entstehen und Vergehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Entre o céu e a terra vida e extinção</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Между небом и землей рождение и гибель</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tra cielo e terra nascita e fine</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">tian di jian sheng yu mie</span></p>
      <p begin="03:39.130" end="03:41.610" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="03:39.130" end="03:39.560">归</span><span begin="03:39.560" end="03:39.880">于</span><span begin="03:39.940" end="03:40.300">尘</span> <span begin="03:40.360" end="03:40.760">归</span><span begin="03:40.760" end="03:41.090">于</span><span begin="03:41.150" end="03:41.610">野</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning to dust returning to the wild</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">塵に帰し 野に帰す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진토(塵土)로 돌아가고, 광야(曠野)로 돌아가네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Retournant à la poussière retournant aux terres sauvages</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Volviendo al polvo volviendo al yermo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zu Staub zerfallend in die Wildnis zurückkehrend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Retornando ao pó retornando à vastidão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Обращаются в прах возвращаются в дикую пустошь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ritornano alla polvere ritornano alla natura selvaggia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">gui yu chen gui yu ye</span></p>
      <p begin="03:44.060" end="03:52.030" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="03:44.060" end="03:45.170">天</span><span begin="03:45.170" end="03:46.220">地</span><span begin="03:46.350" end="03:46.980">间</span> <span begin="03:47.590" end="03:48.080">何</span><span begin="03:48.080" end="03:48.380">为</span><span begin="03:48.430" end="03:48.760">觉</span> <span begin="03:48.830" end="03:50.040">何</span><span begin="03:50.040" end="03:51.040">为</span><span begin="03:51.130" end="03:52.030">解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Between heaven and earth what is awakening what is liberation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">天地の間 何を覚とし 何を解とす</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">천지간 무엇이 깨달음[覺]이며, 무엇이 풀림[解]인가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Entre Ciel et Terre qu'est-ce que l'éveil qu'est-ce que la délivrance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Entre el cielo y la tierra qué es el despertar qué es la liberación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zwischen Himmel und Erde was ist Erwachen was ist Erlösung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Entre o céu e a terra o que é o despertar o que é a libertação</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Между небом и землей в чем истинное пробуждение в чем избавление</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tra cielo e terra cos'è l'illuminazione cos'è la salvezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">tian di jian he wei jue he wei jie</span></p>
      <p begin="03:53.610" end="04:01.600" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="03:53.610" end="03:54.810">生</span><span begin="03:54.810" end="03:55.970">与</span><span begin="03:56.040" end="03:56.580">灭</span> <span begin="03:57.180" end="03:57.620">归</span><span begin="03:57.620" end="03:57.920">于</span><span begin="03:57.980" end="03:58.370">尘</span> <span begin="03:58.430" end="03:59.630">归</span><span begin="03:59.630" end="04:00.830">于</span><span begin="04:00.830" end="04:01.600">野</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Life and extinction returning to dust returning to the wild</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">生と滅 塵に帰し 野に帰す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">생과 멸이여, 진토로 돌아가고, 광야로 돌아가네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Naissance et extinction retournant à la poussière retournant aux terres sauvages</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vida y la extinción volviendo al polvo volviendo al yermo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Entstehen und Vergehen zu Staub zerfallend in die Wildnis zurückkehrend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vida e extinção retornando ao pó retornando à vastidão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рождение и гибель обращаются в прах возвращаются в дикую пустошь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nascita e fine ritornano alla polvere ritornano alla natura selvaggia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sheng yu mie gui yu chen gui yu ye</span></p>
